{"tid":2295673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港醫療系統因為武肺而崩潰會點？","createTime":"2020-11-22T03:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T17:18:09.000Z","uid":57308,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"20f3b72fc2dedbda59020351d97cbad13ae125a6","tid":2295673,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"真係超級大爆發嘅話<br />\n引入大劣醫護就唔洗講啦<br />\n但香港都冇咁多病床病房收病人<br />\n會唔會一車車港豬運上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係大爆發<br />\n後生嘅大多數都頂到<br />\n係班愛国廢老唔知頂唔頂到<br />\n算唔算真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933bdf40e7e1cd4f229cb903ba6639a5178a8482","tid":2295673,"uid":57308,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"香港人冇必要再配合垃圾政府做防疫工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2295237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2295237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 講得幾好<br />\n明明香港人經過03廣東送大禮之後係全球自發防疫做得最好<br />\n俾個正苦害撚到咁<br />\n其實已經仁至義盡"},{"pid":"45b51460b84f127f2f014466badc32af971b3877","tid":2295673,"uid":103759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 反正中咗武肺會有$5000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5a62120bb4a00bd4788e2ef595cf26f4540a35","tid":2295673,"uid":281417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"可能居家隔離算"},{"pid":"dc7fc7b99a8b454eac3b0ef66affb8b53c6b79bc","tid":2295673,"uid":318718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"中央救港<br />\n香港醫護換血"},{"pid":"965d4ac9cbd2de936212273a6acadd861c5cbb7b","tid":2295673,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45b51460b84f127f2f014466badc32af971b3877","tid